{"tid":1255800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講好左 不割𥱊 不內控 只需檢討再Move On","createTime":"2019-06-24T16:11:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T16:28:42.000Z","uid":240319,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e180114635efebafd2275ffa61312273f868320e","tid":1255800,"uid":240319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:11:14.000Z","msg":"本人絕對感激所有義市既付出 冇人有資格屌為香港付出嘅人<br />\n<br />\n但同時希望大家明白 呢度嘅人咁激動嘅意見 只係緊張呢個活動同心痛義士俾對家乘機抹黑 呢度有好多有智慧同埋有社會經驗嘅人 所有意見都值得聽一聽<br />\n<br />\n冇嘢係非黑即白 呢度既智囊團有成千上萬 10個臭和尚點都勝過一個諸葛亮一定打得贏政府個垃圾智囊團 <br />\n<br />\n政府諗緊咩你估我地唔知咩 唔好針對普通市民住 始終不合作運動要用好多文宣資源同時間去解釋同Educate 一般市民 <br />\n<br />\n以我哋而家有限嘅資源同時間 建議聚焦返向主要政權施壓<br />\n<br />\n626 627係G20前最重要一擊 我哋要保持隊形 香港人加油💪🏻"},{"pid":"9b444e566dfb111aaad8a2a5aa2d9ae2c48e2a65","tid":1255800,"uid":240319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:13:44.000Z","msg":"第一次出post 原來吹水台真係咁快沈底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efb1cfedc635ccc42c5e24c4186b9ed8283d0c0","tid":1255800,"uid":240319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:15:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80ffdf52b7c7b7cebbce44c1c91aaae1eac2f9f6","tid":1255800,"uid":240319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:17:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be80362e3c82371ef7c90561097676fd5beed3da","tid":1255800,"uid":240319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:17:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed478179c7aed5f5f48b501257040888c944a6c6","tid":1255800,"uid":240319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28b5d521ea0e892f7ea4c0b300d0d511696698ea","tid":1255800,"uid":240319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"300adc866751d162bf9a61deffd13b66b152ae77","tid":1255800,"uid":240319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pi